result.title: Round 355 Video Tutorial
result.content:
I have been trying to document what I am doing with computer science. If it happens to help someone that is awesome too! So for the last round, I created three videos one for each problem I solved. I also include my reasoning for what I did and try to explain what is wrong and right.

I know that these may not be be the best solutions, but they are working solutions.
